message.content: cs.IT, cs.IT is the most likely category as the paper deals with information theory and mutual information. Other likely categories could be cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) as the paper talks about Markov chains, cs.SY (systems and control) as the paper deals with Gaussian vectors, cs.LG (machine learning) as mutual information is a common measure in machine learning, and cs.MM (multimedia) as the paper talks about source coding.
